Class XSFacets

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.ext.xerces.impl.dv.XSFacets
public class XSFacets extends Object
The class used to pass all facets to XSSimpleType.applyFacets(org.apache.jena.ext.xerces.impl.dv.XSFacets, short, short, org.apache.jena.ext.xerces.impl.dv.ValidationContext). @xerces.internal
